For Extended Range III, get a Supple Scale Armband.  It drops in KC and is No Drop.<br>
<br>
You can get an Amulet of Insight from Thurgadin, 1 group is not able to do this kill but it is purchasable.  This has Extended Enhancment III.<br>
<br>
For Mana Preservation III, you can get an Obulus Death Shroud.  They drop in Old Sebillis.<br>
<br>
There is a new PoP crafted item with a IV focus that I forget.  It did not seems that useful as I recall.<br>
<br>
Most III and IV items worth owning are no drops off of very hard mobs.<br>
<br>
