<br>
Enhancement Haste IV:  You will need to fight in poI till you get 2 Sillicorosive Grease(rare) and Moonstone Crystals(common).   Add a Raw Diamond, and a GM potter can make you a Ceramic Hammer of Innovation.<br>
<br>
Affliction Efficiency III:  Robe of Misery.  You will need to find an Iksar GM tailor for this one.  The hardest piece to get would be Words of Misery.<br>
<br>
Extended Range III:  Drachnid Thyxl  in Dreadlands, or Supple Scale Armband in Karnors.  Thyxl you likely can camp solo.  Drops from Dread Widow(lvl 47-49 mob), SK, have your rune up.   Good course would probably be charm a Ravishing Drovlarg and send it against her.<br>
<br>
Improved Damage III:  Robe of Tempest.  You'll need to find an Erudite GM tailor, and obtain a Rune of Tempest somewhere.<br>
<br>
Mana Preservation III:  Obulus Death Shroud.   Around 20kpp on Xev, rare random drop in Sebilis.   There is also Helm of Nocturnal Phantasms, but that requires drops from PoN and Crypt of Terris Thule, a lvl 62 chanter with Imbue Nightmare, and a GM jewelcrafter.<br>
<br>
Reagent Conservation III:  Runed Mithril Bracer, drops in Sol B, pick it up while raiding Giants for Rokyl's Crystal.  The going price is ~700pp on Xev.  Or go for Iksar Hide Cap from Chardok.  better stats, but it runs around 3kpp.<br>
